---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Chiron"
  description="Learn about Chiron and our mission to help athletes and fitness enthusiasts achieve their training goals."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        About Chiron
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-indigo max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 text-center">
          Named after the wisest centaur in Greek mythology, Chiron is dedicated to helping athletes and fitness enthusiasts reach their full potential.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We believe that everyone has the potential to achieve their athletic goals. Our mission is to provide expert guidance, science-backed training methods, and actionable advice to help you train smarter and perform better.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Training Articles:</strong> In-depth guides on training methodologies, periodization, and performance optimization.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Blog Posts:</strong> Regular updates on fitness trends, athlete stories, and practical tips.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Newsletter:</strong> Weekly curated content delivered straight to your inbox.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Just as Chiron was known for his wisdom and teaching abilities in Greek mythology, we strive to be your trusted guide in the world of athletic training. We believe in:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Evidence-based training approaches</li>
            <li>• Sustainable progress over quick fixes</li>
            <li>• Individualized guidance for all fitness levels</li>
            <li>• Building a supportive community of athletes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
